create new Project step by step process
--------------------------------------
sudo /opt/lampp/lampp start

cd /opt/lampp/htdocs

composer global require "laravel/installer=~1.1"

youva@youva:/opt/lampp/htdocs$ export PATH="~/.config/composer/vendor/bin:$PATH"

youva@youva:/opt/lampp/htdocs$ composer create-project laravel/laravel Projectsec
youva@youva:/opt/lampp/htdocs/Projectsec$ cp .env.example .env
youva@youva:/opt/lampp/htdocs/Projectsec$ vi .env

(ctrl + z) for removing cmd 

